channel.title: Reasons for "UNABLE" result on Chrono swap?
channel.description:
Learn me a thing or two bois
Attempted swapping a delayed death from Prince to a target of his choosing, but failed twice in a row on 2 diff targets.
What would cause this ability to come back with an "unable" sys message? Twice, for that matter?
Thanks
